i had the strangest dream last nite can anyone tell me what it means i had a dream that my mam had been killed by a man i think car crash but i found out in different places i remember crying in different places one place was our parish church the other was my work the next place was a shopping centre where i saw my old best friend from school and then the last place was the hospital anyway i remember crying the whole time in the dream to the point that people were looking at me strangely and i remember feeling heart broken but the nurse who was looking after my mam kept tellin me that i couldn see her but then she said i could and she brought me to this huge all and there was beds everywere and i saw my mam and she was awake and cuddling my dad and i said i thought u were dead and she said oh they just brought me back for a few minutes im going now in awhile then i remember the nurse saying there was one way to kepp her alive and it was by having surgery on her finger weird i know then i was then i was back in work and the surgeon was ringing me telling me the surgery was too complicated to do and he couldn t do it and i was crying again and i convinced him to do it and then i got an email from the nurse tellin me everythin had gone ok and my mam was ok i know that dream sounded confusin and long winded but i didnt want to leave anythin out in case it was relevant anyone any ideas oh and i forgot to mention throughout this dream my brother made no appearance and wasnt even thought about but the feelings i had throught this dream were so surreal they were so intense ive never had a dream like it before even when i woke up i still felt it you have very strong feelings of love and emotion for your mom and that if anything happened to her that no matter where you were in life or other place you lived you would do every thing possible to be there with her personally i hope she is still alive with you so that can still be that way about the finger thing i might not have 